title: RAGE T.V. Beatles Solo Video Collection
description:
This video collection was bought at a garage sale with a bunch of other videotapes for $1.00.
All the original cassette tape said was "BEATLES RAGE" no date or any more info. I would say it is a low generation T.V. Broadcast late 80&#039;s or early 90&#039;s.
Since I&#039;ve never seen it in circulation, I decided to convert to DVD. I had never seen some of these videos before and I think they are fun to watch- Enjoy
